{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji46","name":"毛泽东全集第46卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji46.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给张维的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给张维的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1963年12月14日）楚珩同志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多次来信并附件都收到了。深情厚意，关心政治、卫生工作和我个【人】养生之法，极为感谢！久未作复，尚气原谅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬祝病体逐渐康复。并问魏夫人好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六三年十二月十四日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]张维，又名张楚珩，湖南浏阳人。早年同毛泽东有较多来往。当时任上海第二军医大学教授。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":12,"day":14}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":153,"page_end":153},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}